### 🏷️ Labels

Suggested labels for this feature request:
- `enhancement` - New feature or request
- `good-first-issue` - Good for newcomers
- `help-wanted` - Extra attention is needed
- `needs-discussion` - Requires community discussion
- `breaking-change` - Would introduce breaking changes
- `active-directory` - AD-specific enhancement
- `powershell-module` - PowerShell module related
- `security-assessment` - Security assessment feature

